                      "type": "textInput",
                      "questionId": "q12",
                      "fieldName": "q12",
                      "attrs": {
                        "name": "q12",
                        "type": "text",
                        "id": "q25_input"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " to find a new nest and efficiently direct the others to go there. The study concluded that the effective implementation of the ants' decision meant that the insects could change homes quickly. The study emphasized the necessity, for people as well as insects, of having active "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "tag": "strong",
                      "attrs": {},
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
